，大部份人都喺勞動人口，平時個運動量大，食返白食嚟補充返日常需要嘅能量。依家你打工仔個個日日要ot坐office邊有時間運動，食就照食咁多，咪易有隱疾囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"根本人體構造係預你大多數時候食唔飽"},{"pid":"30215fdf243498475586fbf95f71b83a357e3373","tid":538820,"uid":838,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dfbd64fa750c98ade0592655a371f54461f700de","tid":538820,"uid":64009,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"一罐可樂=五碗飯<br />\n一碗飯=2罐汽水<br />\n可樂=汽水<br />\n<br />\n媽我好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"可樂=汽水=飯=0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd187bd8a5c2b38043c4393e4c79392074367e0","tid":538820,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講<br />\n<br />\n運動/勞動時的能量，其實就係來自&quot;糖份轉換&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n運動多，身體係會俾訊號胰臟分泌更多胰島素去加速&quot;糖份轉換過程&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n反之少運動，胰臟習慣工作量，就會偷懶殆工，令到糖份轉換就會慢。"},{"pid":"c4019edfed5fbce8f95d21ea2ebe62e433fc7226","tid":538820,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"飲汽水當食飯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97654bf5ae3e8cd73b5b567044a2512d324b4f45","tid":538820,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"吹，繼續吹"},{"pid":"775317a49f87c4550604fa374abb64840d7b6ad7","tid":538820,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"白撚痴研究，講到食白飯=食毒藥咁"},{"pid":"bcc3b2530959cbc64eeaef78317647c31f9b5cfb","tid":538820,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfbd64fa750c98ade0592655a371f54461f700de","tid":538820,"uid":64009,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"一罐可樂=五碗飯<br />\n一碗飯=2罐汽水<br />\n可樂=汽水<br />\n<br />\n媽我好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmo